The travel and financial services company named Steven D. Goldstein president of a new Consumer Financial Services group.
The group will develop existing card-member financial services and Optima card operations, which currently are managed by the international division of the Travel Related Services subsidiary.
The unit also will develop the consumer banking lines managed by American Express Bank.
Mr. Goldstein, 37 years old, most recently was president of Travel Related Services for the United Kingdom and Ireland. 

